column5: For You Lew   This Second One Is Much Better
Cool vids, I love watching underwater videos of fish in their natural habitat.  Mike
LOL, welcome to the jungle? no bites? muskies don`t like rock? glad my boat has never seen a radio! LOL just quick glimpses of ski`s!

Thanks, those were pretty cool.  It just goes to show you that fish are really not as skittish as is thought.  They didn't even move until the camera came right up and banged on them.  Interesting.  Joey
